---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Antarctica DAO Roadmap">
    <main>
        <h1 class="text-gradient">Antarctica DAO: Pioneering the Future of the Farcaster Ecosystem</h1>
        
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p><span class="bold">Antarctica DAO</span> is a decentralized autonomous organization dedicated to fostering innovation, growth, and sustainability within the Farcaster ecosystem. By leveraging the collective intelligence and resources of our global community, we aim to support projects, developers, and initiatives that align with the vision of a decentralized social network.</p>
        
        <h2>Mission</h2>
        <p>Our mission is to create a vibrant and self-sustaining Farcaster ecosystem by:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><span class="bold">Investing</span> in promising projects and startups.</li>
            <li><span class="bold">Supporting</span> developers and creators with grants and resources.</li>
            <li><span class="bold">Promoting</span> collaboration and knowledge sharing.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Core Objectives</h2>
        
        <h3>1. Strategic Investments</h3>
        <p>Antarctica DAO seeks to identify and invest in early-stage projects that demonstrate potential for significant impact within the Farcaster ecosystem. By providing financial support and strategic guidance, we aim to accelerate the development and adoption of innovative solutions.</p>
        
        <h3>2. Developer Support</h3>
        <p>We recognize that developers are the backbone of the Farcaster ecosystem. Our DAO provides grants, technical resources, and mentorship to empower developers to create robust and scalable applications. We also organize hackathons, workshops, and other events to foster a collaborative environment.</p>
        
        <h3>3. Ecosystem Growth</h3>
        <p>To ensure the long-term success of Farcaster, Antarctica DAO focuses on initiatives that drive user adoption and engagement. This includes marketing campaigns, educational programs, and partnerships with other organizations that share our vision of a decentralized digital future.</p>
        
        <h2>Governance Model</h2>
        <p>Antarctica DAO operates on a fully decentralized governance model, ensuring that all members have a voice in decision-making processes. Key features include:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><span class="bold">Token-based Voting</span>: Members hold governance tokens that allow them to vote on proposals and initiatives.</li>
            <li><span class="bold">Transparent Processes</span>: All decisions and transactions are recorded on-chain, providing full transparency and accountability.</li>
            <li><span class="bold">Community-driven Proposals</span>: Any member can submit proposals, ensuring a diverse range of ideas and initiatives.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Why Farcaster?</h2>
        <p>Farcaster represents a new era of decentralized social networking, where users have control over their data and interactions. By supporting the Farcaster ecosystem, Antarctica DAO is contributing to the creation of a more open, fair, and user-centric internet.</p>
        
        <h2>Join Us</h2>
        <p>We invite developers, investors, and enthusiasts to join Antarctica DAO and be part of this exciting journey. Together, we can build a thriving ecosystem that empowers individuals and communities around the world.</p>
        
        <h3>How to Get Involved</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><span class="bold">Become a Member</span>: Acquire governance tokens and participate in our decision-making processes.</li>
            <li><span class="bold">Submit Proposals</span>: Share your ideas for projects and initiatives that can benefit the Farcaster ecosystem.</li>
            <li><span class="bold">Collaborate</span>: Partner with us on events, research, and other activities to drive ecosystem growth.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Conclusion</h2>
        <p>Antarctica DAO is more than just an investment vehicle; it is a community-driven initiative committed to the long-term success of the Farcaster ecosystem. By bringing together a diverse group of stakeholders, we aim to create a sustainable and innovative environment where decentralized social networking can thrive.</p>
        <p>Join us in shaping the future of Farcaster. Together, we can make a difference.</p>

        <div class="button-container">
            <a href="/" class="back-button">Back to Startpage</a>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    main {
        margin: auto;
        padding: 1rem;
        width: 800px;
        max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
        color: #e2e8f0; /* Snow blue color */
        font-size: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .astro-a {
        position: absolute;
        top: -32px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translatex(-50%);
        width: 220px;
        height: auto;
        z-index: -1;
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 4rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1em;
    }
    .text-gradient {
        background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #a5b4fc, #c4b5fd); /* Pastel blue gradient */
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-size: 400%;
        background-position: 0%;
    }
    .instructions {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(197, 212, 235, 0.25); /* Light snow blue with 25% opacity */
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(167, 189, 245, 0.66), rgba(201, 193, 253, 0.33)); /* Pastel blue gradient */
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .instructions code {
        font-size: 0.8em;
        font-weight: bold;
        background: rgba(197, 212, 235, 0.12); /* Light snow blue with 12% opacity */
        color: #e2e8f0; /* Snow blue color */
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 0.3em 0.4em;
    }
    .instructions strong {
        color: #e2e8f0; /* Snow blue color */
    }
    .link-card-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        padding: 0;
    }
    h2, h3 {
        color: #2c3e50;
    }
    h2 {
        font-size: 2em;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    h3 {
        font-size: 1.5em;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    ul {
        list-style-type: disc;
        margin-left: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    ul li {
        margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .bold {
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    .button-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .back-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #e2e8f0;
        background-color: #2c3e50;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .back-button:hover {
        background-color: #1a202c;
    }
</style>
